<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     TECHNOLOGY
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="about-section about-tech">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
        <div class="about-section-img">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620712943543-bcc4688e7485?w=640&q=80"
                 alt="AI neural network architecture visualisation" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-section-text">
            <span class="section-tag tag-purple">Technology Stack</span>
            <h2>A Hybrid Architecture Built for Real-World Deployment</h2>
            <p>
                Skinalyze uses a three-layer hybrid architecture: a Python-based ML microservice
                for inference, a .NET Core frontend and backend for user interaction and
                business logic, and a connected cloud-hosted dataset pipeline for training
                and preprocessing.
            </p>
            <p>
                The AI layer evaluates multiple state-of-the-art CNN architectures —
                MobileNetV2, EfficientNetB1, InceptionV3 — selecting the best-performing
                model per prediction. Grad-CAM converts the internal decision process
                into a human-readable heatmap. The RAG chatbot indexes medical documents
                into a FAISS vector database and performs restricted-domain internet
                lookups to answer contextual queries.
            </p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
                <span>Python</span>
                <span>TensorFlow / Keras</span>
                <span>PyTorch</span>
                <span>EfficientNet</span>
                <span>MobileNetV2</span>
                <span>InceptionV3</span>
                <span>Grad-CAM</span>
                <span>LangChain</span>
                <span>FAISS</span>
                <span>HuggingFace</span>
                <span>ASP.NET Core (.NET 6+)</span>
                <span>Flask / FastAPI</span>
                <span>QuestPDF</span>
                <span>Cloud Storage</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     AGILE PROCESS
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="about-section" style="background:#f7faf8;">
    <div class="about-section-inner reverse">
        <div class="about-section-img">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611532736597-de2d4265fba3?w=640&q=80"
                 alt="Team collaboration on software development" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-section-text">
            <span class="section-tag tag-pink">Development Process</span>
            <h2>Built Using an Agile Incremental Model</h2>
            <p>
                The Agile Incremental model was selected due to the project's need for iterative
                development, continuous model improvement, and progressive integration of the ML
                system, chatbot, and web application across four structured iterations.
            </p>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li><strong>Iteration 1:</strong> ML model training &amp; REST API setup</li>
                <li><strong>Iteration 2:</strong> .NET frontend &amp; backend development</li>
                <li><strong>Iteration 3:</strong> RAG chatbot integration (LangChain + FAISS)</li>
                <li><strong>Iteration 4:</strong> PDF report generation module</li>
                <li><strong>Final:</strong> Full integration, system testing &amp; deployment</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

